{
  "_comment": "sovereign-os IPS host overview — operator-at-a-glance cockpit consolidating ALL 8 observability verticals shipped to date (M060 + MS022 + four-watchdog + modules + daemon-process + AppArmor + auth-events + systemd-units). Consumes the cross-vertical recording rules from config/prometheus/rules/sovereign-os-observability-rollup.yml (commit 594fd02) plus per-vertical headline gauges from the 8 selfdef-side textfile observers. Single-pane-of-glass — operators see the IPS host's entire defensive posture without drilling into per-vertical dashboards. Project boundary R10212: pure read-only observability composition.",
  "annotations": {"list": []},
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 0,
  "id": null,
  "links": [
